
"smart_sources:RemNoteExport_xdf--math_md_2026-01-29_04-43/pin/xdf 讲义/25高三\u0001寒假行远/03函数的图像与零点问题.md": {"path":"RemNoteExport_xdf--math_md_2026-01-29_04-43/pin/xdf 讲义/25高三\u0001寒假行远/03函数的图像与零点问题.md","last_embed":{"hash":null},"embeddings":{},"last_read":{"hash":"17dynqe","at":1769676327884},"class_name":"SmartSource","last_import":{"mtime":1761290408000,"size":16983,"at":1769676327884,"hash":"17dynqe"},"blocks":{"#":[1,246],"##{1}":[1,10],"##{2}":[116,221],"##{3}":[222,246]},"outlinks":[{"title":"图像变换","target":"../../../图像变换.md","line":1},{"title":"分式函数","target":"../../../分式函数.md","line":33},{"title":"中心对称","target":"../../../中心对称.md","line":38},{"title":"三角函数","target":"../../../三角函数.md","line":44},{"title":"图像判断","target":"../../../图像判断.md","line":54},{"title":"零点问题","target":"../../../零点.md","line":116},{"title":"0,1) \\\\ 1-|x-3|, x \\in[1,+\\infty)\\end{array}\\right.$, 则关于 $x$ 的函数 $F(x)=f(x)-a(0<a<1)$ 的所有零点之和为 $\\qquad$ （结果用 $a$ 表示）。\n            - \n        - 练 9-2\n            - \n            - 已知函数 $f(x)=\\left\\{\\begin{array}{l}e^{(x+1)^{2}}, x \\leqslant 0 \\\\ x+\\frac{4}{x}-3, x>0\\end{array}\\right.$, 函数 $y=f(x)-a$ 有四个不同零点, 从小到大依次为 $x_{1}, x_{2}$, $x_{3}, x_{4}$ ，则 $x_{1} x_{2}+x_{3} x_{4}$ 的取值范围为 $\\qquad$ .\n            - \n        - 例 10\n            - \n            - 已知函数 $f(x)=\\left|\\log _{a}\\right| 1-x| |(a>0, a \\neq 1)$, 若 $x_{1}<x_{2}<x_{3}<x_{4}$,\n            - 且 $f\\left(x_{1}\\right)=f\\left(x_{2}\\right)=f\\left(x_{3}\\right)=f\\left(x_{4}\\right)$, 则 $\\frac{1}{x_{1}}+\\frac{1}{x_{2}}+\\frac{1}{x_{3}}+\\frac{1}{x_{4}}=$ $\\qquad$ .\n            - \n        - 练 10-1\n            - \n            - 已知函数 $f(x)=\\left\\{\\begin{array}{l}\\left|\\log _{4} x\\right|, 0<x<4 \\\\ \\cos \\left(\\frac{\\pi x}{2}\\right), 4 \\leqslant x \\leqslant 8\\end{array}\\right.$, 若存在实数 $x_{1}, x_{2}, x_{3}, x_{4}$ 满足 $x_{1}<x_{2}<x_{3}<x_{4}$, 且 $f\\left(x_{1}\\right)=f\\left(x_{2}\\right)=f\\left(x_{3}\\right)=f\\left(x_{4}\\right)$, 则 $x_{1} x_{2} x_{3} x_{4}$ 的取值范围为 $\\qquad$ .\n            - \n        - 练 10-2\n            - \n            - 设函数 $f(x)=\\left\\{\\begin{array}{l}-x^{2}-2 x, x \\leqslant 0 \\\\ |\\ln x|, x>0\\end{array}\\right.$, 现有如下命题, (1)若方程 $f(x)=a$ 有四个不同的实根 $x_{1} 、 x_{2}$ 、 $x_{3} 、 x_{4}$, 则 $x_{1} \\cdot x_{2} \\cdot x_{3} \\cdot x_{4}$ 的取值范围是 $(0,1)$; (2)方程 $f^{2}(x)-\\left(a+\\frac{1}{a}\\right) f(x)+1=0$ 的不同实根的个数只能是 $1,2,3,8$. 下列判断正确的是（）\n            - A. (1)和(2)均为真命题\n            - B. (1)和(2)均为假命题\n            - C. (1)为真命题，(2)为假命题\n            - D. (1)为假命题，(2)为真命题\n        - \n- [03函数的图像与零点问题","target":"03函数的图像与零点问题.md","line":199},{"title":"绝对值函数","target":"../../../绝对值函数.md","line":228},{"title":"分段函数","target":"../../../分段函数.md","line":232},{"title":"绝对值讨论","target":"../../../绝对值讨论.md","line":232}],"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[]},
