}{x_{4}}=$ $\\qquad$ .\n            - \n        - 练 10-1\n            - \n            - 已知函数 $f(x)=\\left\\{\\begin{array}{l}\\left|\\log _{4} x\\right|, 0<x<4 \\\\ \\cos \\left(\\frac{\\pi x}{2}\\right), 4 \\leqslant x \\leqslant 8\\end{array}\\right.$, 若存在实数 $x_{1}, x_{2}, x_{3}, x_{4}$ 满足 $x_{1}<x_{2}<x_{3}<x_{4}$, 且 $f\\left(x_{1}\\right)=f\\left(x_{2}\\right)=f\\left(x_{3}\\right)=f\\left(x_{4}\\right)$, 则 $x_{1} x_{2} x_{3} x_{4}$ 的取值范围为 $\\qquad$ .\n            - \n        - 练 10-2\n            - \n            - 设函数 $f(x)=\\left\\{\\begin{array}{l}-x^{2}-2 x, x \\leqslant 0 \\\\ |\\ln x|, x>0\\end{array}\\right.$, 现有如下命题, (1)若方程 $f(x)=a$ 有四个不同的实根 $x_{1} 、 x_{2}$ 、 $x_{3} 、 x_{4}$, 则 $x_{1} \\cdot x_{2} \\cdot x_{3} \\cdot x_{4}$ 的取值范围是 $(0,1)$; (2)方程 $f^{2}(x)-\\left(a+\\frac{1}{a}\\right) f(x)+1=0$ 的不同实根的个数只能是 $1,2,3,8$. 下列判断正确的是（）\n            - A. (1)和(2)均为真命题\n            - B. (1)和(2)均为假命题\n            - C. (1)为真命题，(2)为假命题\n            - D. (1)为假命题，(2)为真命题\n        - \n- [03函数的图像与零点问题","target":"03函数的图像与零点问题.md","line":199},{"title":"绝对值函数","target":"../../../绝对值函数.md","line":228},{"title":"分段函数","target":"../../../分段函数.md","line":232},{"title":"绝对值讨论","target":"../../../绝对值讨论.md","line":232}],"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"last_embed":{"hash":"17dynqe","at":1769676516947}},"smart_blocks:RemNoteExport_xdf--math_md_2026-01-29_04-43/pin/xdf 讲义/25高三\u0001寒假行远/03函数的图像与零点问题.md#": {"path":null,"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.07712065,-0.04224097,0.07203419,-0.02658367,-0.00269659,-0.00956068,-0.05367059,0.02129032,0.05216337,-0.0060954,0.01436277,-0.062344,0.06596373,-0.0127126,0.01078017,-0.00322677,-0.00814637,-0.01603456,-0.0698994,-0.03379361,0.11165556,-0.03753971,-0.00275608,-0.06646103,0.04050242,0.03735882,-0.01702486,-0.01910668,-0.02416931,-0.19229871,-0.02190739,0.00954829,0.00271376,0.00974881,0.03855523,-0.07395694,-0.04829258,0.04058,-0.0135445,0.05975037,-0.02068873,0.04902379,0.0308992,-0.00206797,0.00052758,-